Working with dates in accounting

The current tutorial is inspired by the current (March) issue of the CPA Australia journal #InTheBlack which demonstrates how to use date formats in Excel. An image below is a snippet of the article.

I thought it is a good idea to write a tutorial to show how the same approach can be used in R. Leaving judgements on appropriateness of either, Excel or R for the task on hand, lets dig into this.

We are going to work with a dataset of transactions from Kaggle.
